43
00:03:00,130 --> 00:03:01,130
Hold on to me.

44
00:03:01,130 --> 00:03:02,130
I don't trust you.

45
00:03:02,130 --> 00:03:03,130
I don't know.

46
00:03:03,130 --> 00:03:04,130
Slowly.

47
00:03:10,130 --> 00:03:11,130
Clara.

48
00:03:11,130 --> 00:03:12,130
