49
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:13,130
Please say something.

50
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:14,130
Grandfather, quick!

51
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:16,130
Come on, help!

52
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:17,130
Is it bad?

53
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,130
No, it's not.

54
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:20,130
Clara.

55
00:03:24,916 --> 00:03:27,916
