70
00:04:02,202 --> 00:04:04,802
Clara's legs are not used to running yet.

71
00:04:05,202 --> 00:04:07,002
Now don't let yourself be discouraged.

72
00:04:07,202 --> 00:04:09,402
We're starting slowly, step by step.

73
00:04:09,602 --> 00:04:11,802
This won't work overnight.

74
