77
00:04:37,156 --> 00:04:39,156
Very good. Really excellent.

78
00:04:39,156 --> 00:04:41,156
I was afraid you didn't feel anything at all.

79
00:04:41,156 --> 00:04:43,156
I would have preferred that.

80
