One, two, one, two, one, two, one, two.

87
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:00,410
Very slowly, Heidi.

88
00:05:00,410 --> 00:05:01,850
The way I did it.

89
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:03,210
One after the other.

90
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:04,570
Mhm.

91
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:09,210
One, two, one, two.

92
00:05:09,210 --> 00:05:10,890
Like this?

93
00:05:10,890 --> 00:05:12,250
Yes, that's right.

94
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:13,690
Slowly and evenly.

95
00:05:13,690 --> 00:05:14,490
Is that clear?

96
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:16,290
And how long is it?

97
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:17,530
As long as you can.

98
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:18,730
I'll call you then.

99
00:05:18,730 --> 00:05:19,530
Good.

100
00:05:20,218 --> 00:05:24,218
