Ah, then of course we can't.

112
00:05:56,796 --> 00:05:58,196
We'll be late by tonight!

113
00:05:58,196 --> 00:05:59,396
Good morning, everyone!

114
00:05:59,396 --> 00:06:01,196
Watch out for the goats!

115
00:06:01,196 --> 00:06:03,796
Yes, and give the ghost a herb! You know why!

116
00:06:03,796 --> 00:06:05,996
I want it to be the best milk in the world!

117
00:06:05,996 --> 00:06:07,396
You don't have to tell me!

118
00:06:07,396 --> 00:06:08,676
Goodbye!

119
00:06:08,676 --> 00:06:10,916
I promise we'll practice hard!

120
00:06:10,916 --> 00:06:12,916
Puppet light! Go!

121
00:06:13,716 --> 00:06:15,716
Let's keep going!

122
