240
00:15:32,756 --> 00:15:34,756
Otherwise you wouldn't have come.

241
00:15:34,756 --> 00:15:38,756
Michael, bring me the butter we just made.

242
00:15:38,756 --> 00:15:42,756
Look at this. What does it look like? Huh?

243
00:15:42,756 --> 00:15:47,074
Hmm. Yes, quite decent. Tell me.

244
00:15:47,074 --> 00:15:50,074
Why don't you repair your pot? The water's running out.

245
00:15:50,074 --> 00:15:53,074
I know. I just didn't get the hang of it.

246
00:15:53,074 --> 00:15:58,074
I'll make you an offer. I'll repair the pot, and you'll give me the butter.

247
00:15:58,074 --> 00:16:01,074
Yes, I have nothing against it.

248
00:16:01,074 --> 00:16:03,074
Strange.

249
00:16:10,364 --> 00:16:12,364
Why doesn't he take his own butter?

250
00:16:12,364 --> 00:16:15,364
I think he needs ours for the maimed girl from Frankfurt,

251
00:16:15,364 --> 00:16:17,364
